            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In nomine Dei eterni. Anno eiusdem incarnacionis millesimo C XXV,
                        indicione tercia, XIIII die exeunte mensis madii. Constat me <persName
                            key="#marriage #Salian #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Hay/fodder #Animals #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#people/3565">Albericus</persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Lombard #Salian #kinOf #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Hay/fodder #Animals #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ><name ref="Cunitia">Cuniza</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">iugalibus</rs>, que profesa sum lex nanacione mea lege
                        vivere <rs key="#Lombard">Lonbarda</rs>, set nu[n]c pro ipso viro meo lege
                        videor vivere <rs key="#Salian">Salica</rs>, presens presentibus diesise:
                        melius est homo metu mortis vivere quam spe vivendi morte subitanea
                        prevenire. Qua pro[p]ter causa Dei omnipotentis ac pro anima nostra mercede,
                        consenciente Alberico viro meo et subter confirmate, una cum noticia de <rs
                            key="#kinOf">propinquis parentibus</rs> meis, et est <persName
                            key="#kinOf #Witness"><name ref="Federicus">Fedricus</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#kinOf"><name ref="Otto">Oto</name></persName>, vobis
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3538">Poncio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abati</rs> de <placeName key="#Abbots" ref="#places/4108"
                            >Camposion</placeName> et venerabi[li] loco <orgName
                            key="#Abbots #Missus #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Hay/fodder #Animals #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2420">Scante Cruce</orgName> ceterisque
                        fratribus illuc Deo servientibus, in Collomano miso vesstro per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam donacionis et obfercionis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Public_rituals #Salian">cum cultello, atrementario, penna, festuca
                            notata, ramum arboris, vuantonern et vuasasonem terre</rs>, certam in
                        vobis facimus investituram et tradicione, nominative de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">masio uno</rs> in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/125"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/13"
                            >Tarvisiano</placeName></geogName> in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Avax</placeName> iuris nostri, quam
                        supradictam masariciam nobis <persName key="#Missus"><name ref="Collomanno"
                                >Collomanno</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Missus">miso</rs> Poncio abati trado, obfero per cartulam
                        donacionis et obfercionis in vobis abendai confirmo, una cum acesionisbusc
                        et ingresionibus seu cum superioribus, <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals"
                            >pasculis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Legumes">campiis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">pisscacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venacionibus</rs>, cultis
                        et incultis, divisis et [in]divisis, nulli alii tradita, donata, obxiata
                        nisi vobis, faciatis vos et sucesores vest[r]os iure proprietari nomine
                        quiquid volueritis si[ne] nostro et [he]redurm nostrum contradicione. Quidem
                        spondimus atque promittimus vobis Collomanno miso Poncio abati una cum meis
                        heredibus ac proheredibus defensare; quod si defensare non potuerimus aut si
                        vobis a aliquid per quovix ingenium ullamquis ocasione sutraere quesierimus,
                        nobis in diplum restue sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata au[t] valuerit
                        su[b] exstimacione [in] consimili loco; et obbligamus pena que est <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri obtimi uncias X argenti pondera xx</rs>, et quod
                        [requesie ]rimus vendicare non valeamus, set prese[ns] obfercio stabilis
                        persistat cum stipulacione [ ... ] subnixa. Actum in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4110">Solaga</placeName> felliciter. +++ manu donatoris
                        obfertoris qui hac cartulam fieri rogavit. [ ... ] [<rs key="#Witness"
                            >te]stium</rs> in[ter]fuerunt Fedricus, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Conradus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ref="#people/3577">Ianatas</persName> [ ... ] <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Amelricus">Almericus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Ceso">Ceso</name></persName>
                        interfuerunt. Quidem ego <persName key="#Judge #Notary #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Ardericus">Ardericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> traditam
                        complevi. </ab>
